author: Minecraft
description:
Minecraft has entered The Copper Age! Express yourself in every shade of copper as you transform this versatile metal into handy tools, shiny armor, gleaming light sources, oxidizing decor, smart storage, and even lively mechanical companions known as copper golems. Whether scraped or oxidized, this is the start of a new clonking era of creativity!

author: Minecraft
description:
The Copper Age is coming to all Minecraft platforms on September 30! To celebrate the occasion, The Deep Dig unleashes the creativity of Minecraft creators Shubble and Mogswamp who show us how to incorporate all the new building blocks from THE COPPER AGE with both intricate designs and mad machinations!
